        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Darren Drake Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Transportation Security Administration to disseminate and periodically update best practices for vehicle rental companies and dealers to report suspicious behavior to law enforcement to prevent vehicle ramming and other terrorist attacks.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
